<figureCitation box="[160,247,404,431]" captionStart="FIGURE 5" captionStartId="46.[151,250,1799,1824]" captionTargetBox="[166,1420,181,1763]" captionTargetId="figure@46.[151,1435,166,1779]" captionTargetPageId="46" captionText="FIGURE 5. Selected Portuguese species. A. Neurigona biflexa (♂); B. Orthoceratium sabulosum (♂); C. Parathalassius blasigii (♂); D. Poecilobothrus nobilitatus (♂); E. Rhaphium appendiculatum (♂); F. Rhaphium brevicorne (♂); G. Rhaphium longicorne (♂); H. Rhaphium micans (♂); I. Schoenophilus versutus (♂); J. Sciapus albovittatus (♂); K. Sciapus laetus (♂); L. Sciapus pallens (♂); M. Sciapus platypterus (♂); N. Sciapus zonatulus (♂); O. Sybistroma dufourii (♂); photos by Rui Andrade, except for D by James A.C. Clark." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3357633/files/figure.png" pageId="47" pageNumber="48">Fig. 5D</figureCitation>
